  "text": "In this study, GO was synthesized by an improved Hummers method [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Carbon components (0.5 mg/mL) and H 2 PtCl 6 (0.5 mg/mL) were ultrasonicated with DI water for 30 min. The weight ratio of rGO to CB as the hybrid support was arranged as shown in Table 1 . The synthesis of the hybrid electrocatalysts was explained in our previous study [CITATION_3] .",
